fill your electric kettle
turn it on
wait for boiling in 100 degree
add it to the pot
pot on the flame to the maximum
add coarse salt and oil
if it is boiling add your pasta
if it is not turn back to number 3
test your pasta to be sure is al dente
if it is was not wait 3 minutes
when the pasta is al dente , drip the pasta with a colander
add tomato sause 
you can have your pasta
